      <div class="advc-faq-with-content-item advc-faq-with-nav-text-item__block nsa-accesstive" data-open="0">
        <div class="advc-faq-with-nav-text-item__block-title nsa-accesstive">
          <div class="advc-sub-title nsa-accesstive">What is the Yarbo 5-Year Pledge Campaign?</div>
          <div class="advc-faq-with-nav-text-item__block-open-icon nsa-accesstive">
            <svg fill="none" height="16" viewbox="0 0 16 16" width="16" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <path d="M0 8H16M8 0L8 16" stroke="black" stroke-width="2"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="advc-faq-with-nav-text-item__block-close-icon advc-d-none nsa-accesstive">
            <svg fill="none" height="2" viewbox="0 0 16 2" width="16" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <path d="M0 1H16" stroke="black" stroke-width="2"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div
          class="advc-faq-with-nav-text-item__block-desc advc-body advc-richtext nsa-accesstive"
          style="height: 0px; opacity: 0; margin-top: 0px;"
        >
          <strong class="nsa-accesstive">A:</strong> This campaign offers eligible customers a complimentary YarboCare™
          Worry-Free Plan when purchasing qualifying Yarbo products. The plan includes 5 years of warranty coverage, 3
          years of accidental protection, and shipping protection at no additional cost.
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="advc-faq-with-content-item advc-faq-with-nav-text-item__block nsa-accesstive" data-open="0">
        <div class="advc-faq-with-nav-text-item__block-title nsa-accesstive">
          <div class="advc-sub-title nsa-accesstive">When does this campaign run and are there quantity limits?</div>
          <div class="advc-faq-with-nav-text-item__block-open-icon nsa-accesstive">
            <svg fill="none" height="16" viewbox="0 0 16 16" width="16" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <path d="M0 8H16M8 0L8 16" stroke="black" stroke-width="2"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="advc-faq-with-nav-text-item__block-close-icon advc-d-none nsa-accesstive">
            <svg fill="none" height="2" viewbox="0 0 16 2" width="16" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <path d="M0 1H16" stroke="black" stroke-width="2"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div
          class="advc-faq-with-nav-text-item__block-desc advc-body advc-richtext nsa-accesstive"
          style="height: 0px; opacity: 0; margin-top: 0px;"
        >
          <strong class="nsa-accesstive">A:</strong> The campaign runs from August 15-31, 2025. The offer is limited to
          the first 500 qualifying Yarbo products sold. Once this limit is reached, the campaign will end regardless of
          whether the time period has concluded.
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="advc-faq-with-content-item advc-faq-with-nav-text-item__block nsa-accesstive" data-open="0">
        <div class="advc-faq-with-nav-text-item__block-title nsa-accesstive">
          <div class="advc-sub-title nsa-accesstive">Who is eligible for this offer?</div>
          <div class="advc-faq-with-nav-text-item__block-open-icon nsa-accesstive">
            <svg fill="none" height="16" viewbox="0 0 16 16" width="16" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <path d="M0 8H16M8 0L8 16" stroke="black" stroke-width="2"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="advc-faq-with-nav-text-item__block-close-icon advc-d-none nsa-accesstive">
            <svg fill="none" height="2" viewbox="0 0 16 2" width="16" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <path d="M0 1H16" stroke="black" stroke-width="2"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div
          class="advc-faq-with-nav-text-item__block-desc advc-body advc-richtext nsa-accesstive"
          style="height: 0px; opacity: 0; margin-top: 0px;"
        >
          <strong class="nsa-accesstive">A:</strong> This offer is available to new customers in the United States and
          Canada who purchase qualifying products directly from our official website (<a
            class="underline"
            href="https://www.yarbo.com"
            >www.yarbo.com</a
          >). Products must include a Yarbo Core to be eligible. Purchases made through third-party retailers do not
          qualify.
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="advc-faq-with-content-item advc-faq-with-nav-text-item__block nsa-accesstive" data-open="0">
        <div class="advc-faq-with-nav-text-item__block-title nsa-accesstive">
          <div class="advc-sub-title nsa-accesstive">Which products are included in this campaign?</div>
          <div class="advc-faq-with-nav-text-item__block-open-icon nsa-accesstive">
            <svg fill="none" height="16" viewbox="0 0 16 16" width="16" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <path d="M0 8H16M8 0L8 16" stroke="black" stroke-width="2"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="advc-faq-with-nav-text-item__block-close-icon advc-d-none nsa-accesstive">
            <svg fill="none" height="2" viewbox="0 0 16 2" width="16" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <path d="M0 1H16" stroke="black" stroke-width="2"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div
          class="advc-faq-with-nav-text-item__block-desc advc-body advc-richtext nsa-accesstive"
          style="height: 0px; opacity: 0; margin-top: 0px;"
        >
          <strong class="nsa-accesstive">A:</strong> Qualifying products include the Yarbo Core and most of our main
          product lines: lawn mowers, snow blowers, blowers, and various combination packages such as the 4-in-1 Yard
          Robot. Individual accessories are not covered under this offer.
        </div>
      </div>
