      <div class="advc-faq-with-content-item advc-faq-with-nav-text-item__block nsa-accesstive" data-open="0">
        <div class="advc-faq-with-nav-text-item__block-title nsa-accesstive">
          <div class="advc-sub-title nsa-accesstive">What coverage does the YarboCare™ Worry-Free Plan provide?</div>
          <div class="advc-faq-with-nav-text-item__block-open-icon nsa-accesstive">
            <svg fill="none" height="16" viewbox="0 0 16 16" width="16" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <path d="M0 8H16M8 0L8 16" stroke="black" stroke-width="2"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="advc-faq-with-nav-text-item__block-close-icon advc-d-none nsa-accesstive">
            <svg fill="none" height="2" viewbox="0 0 16 2" width="16" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <path d="M0 1H16" stroke="black" stroke-width="2"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div
          class="advc-faq-with-nav-text-item__block-desc advc-body advc-richtext nsa-accesstive"
          style="height: 0px; opacity: 0; margin-top: 0px;"
        >
          <p class="whitespace-normal break-words nsa-accesstive">
            <strong class="nsa-accesstive">A:</strong> The plan includes:
          </p>
          <ul class="[&amp;:not(:last-child)_ul]:pb-1 [&amp;:not(:last-child)_ol]:pb-1 list-disc space-y-1.5 pl-7 nsa-accesstive">
            <li class="whitespace-normal break-words nsa-accesstive">
              <strong class="nsa-accesstive">5-Year Total Warranty</strong>: 2-year standard plus 3-year extended
              coverage for defects and performance issues
            </li>
            <li class="whitespace-normal break-words nsa-accesstive">
              <strong class="nsa-accesstive">3-Year Accidental Protection</strong>: Covers drops, weather damage, and
              electrical surges (excludes normal wear)
            </li>
            <li class="whitespace-normal break-words nsa-accesstive">
              <strong class="nsa-accesstive">Shipping Protection</strong>: Coverage during transit
            </li>
          </ul>
          <p class="whitespace-normal break-words nsa-accesstive">Claims are capped at your actual purchase price.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="advc-faq-with-content-item advc-faq-with-nav-text-item__block nsa-accesstive" data-open="0">
        <div class="advc-faq-with-nav-text-item__block-title nsa-accesstive">
          <div class="advc-sub-title nsa-accesstive">How do I activate the plan and file claims if needed?</div>
          <div class="advc-faq-with-nav-text-item__block-open-icon nsa-accesstive">
            <svg fill="none" height="16" viewbox="0 0 16 16" width="16" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <path d="M0 8H16M8 0L8 16" stroke="black" stroke-width="2"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="advc-faq-with-nav-text-item__block-close-icon advc-d-none nsa-accesstive">
            <svg fill="none" height="2" viewbox="0 0 16 2" width="16" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <path d="M0 1H16" stroke="black" stroke-width="2"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div
          class="advc-faq-with-nav-text-item__block-desc advc-body advc-richtext nsa-accesstive"
          style="height: 0px; opacity: 0; margin-top: 0px;"
        >
          During checkout, the YarboCare™ Worry-Free Plan will automatically appear as a $0 gift item for eligible
          orders. After purchase, you'll receive an email from XCotton with your official policy details. To file a
          claim, use the resolution center link provided in your confirmation email and follow the guided process.
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="advc-faq-with-content-item advc-faq-with-nav-text-item__block nsa-accesstive" data-open="0">
        <div class="advc-faq-with-nav-text-item__block-title nsa-accesstive">
          <div class="advc-sub-title nsa-accesstive">Can this offer be combined with other promotions?</div>
          <div class="advc-faq-with-nav-text-item__block-open-icon nsa-accesstive">
            <svg fill="none" height="16" viewbox="0 0 16 16" width="16" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <path d="M0 8H16M8 0L8 16" stroke="black" stroke-width="2"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="advc-faq-with-nav-text-item__block-close-icon advc-d-none nsa-accesstive">
            <svg fill="none" height="2" viewbox="0 0 16 2" width="16" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <path d="M0 1H16" stroke="black" stroke-width="2"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div
          class="advc-faq-with-nav-text-item__block-desc advc-body advc-richtext nsa-accesstive"
          style="height: 0px; opacity: 0; margin-top: 0px;"
        >
          Combination with other promotions or discounts depends on the specific terms and our checkout system's
          eligibility criteria. Please review the terms at checkout to see what combinations may be available.
        </div>
      </div>
