            </li>
          </ol>
          <p class="nsa-accesstive">
            The Yarbo 5-Year Pledge campaign ("Campaign") is organized by Yarbo ("we," "us," or "our") and offers
            eligible customers a complimentary YarboCare™ Worry-Free Plan when purchasing eligible Yarbo products during
            the Campaign Period.
          </p>
          <p class="nsa-accesstive">
            <strong class="nsa-accesstive">Note:</strong>This offer is limited to the first 500 eligible Yarbo products
            sold during the Campaign Period. Once the limit is reached, the offer will no longer be available, even if
            the Campaign Period has not ended.
          </p>
          <ol class="nsa-accesstive" start="2">
            <li class="nsa-accesstive">
              <span class="nsa-accesstive" style="font-size: 20px;"
                ><strong class="nsa-accesstive">Campaign Period</strong></span
              >
            </li>
          </ol>
          <ul class="nsa-accesstive">
            <li class="nsa-accesstive">
              Valid from August 15, 2025 to August 31, 2025 (both dates inclusive). Outside the Campaign Period, the
              YarboCare™ Product Protection Plan (including accidental protection and extended warranty) and the
              Shipping Protection can be purchased separately at full price.
            </li>
            <li class="nsa-accesstive">Orders must be placed online via Yarbo's official website (www.yarbo.com).</li>
            <li class="nsa-accesstive">
              Purchases made through third-party platforms (e.g., Amazon, other retailers) are not eligible.
            </li>
            <li class="nsa-accesstive">
              Offer applies only while supplies last and is capped at the first 500 Yarbo Core sold.
            </li>
          </ul>
          <ol class="nsa-accesstive" start="3">
            <li class="nsa-accesstive">
              <span class="nsa-accesstive" style="font-size: 20px;"
                ><strong class="nsa-accesstive">Eligibility</strong></span
              >
            </li>
          </ol>
          <ul class="nsa-accesstive">
            <li class="nsa-accesstive">
              The offer is available only to new customers who purchase at least one eligible Yarbo product including a
              Yarbo Core within the Campaign Period.
            </li>
            <li class="nsa-accesstive">
              Eligibility is further restricted to the first 500 Yarbo Core sold; after this limit, the offer will
              automatically expire.
            </li>
            <li class="nsa-accesstive">Eligible territories: United States and Canada only.</li>
          </ul>
          <ol class="nsa-accesstive" start="4">
            <li class="nsa-accesstive">
              <span class="nsa-accesstive" style="font-size: 20px;"
                ><strong class="nsa-accesstive">Eligible Products</strong></span
              >
            </li>
          </ol>
          <p class="nsa-accesstive">
            The following products qualify for the Campaign when purchased via Yarbo's official website during the
            Campaign Period:
