          <ol class="nsa-accesstive">
            <li class="nsa-accesstive"><strong class="nsa-accesstive">YarboCare™ Worry-Free Plan</strong></li>
          </ol>
          <p class="nsa-accesstive">
            The YarboCare™ Worry-Free Plan is administered by XCotton, our official product protection provider, and
            <a href="https://www.aig.com/"><u>underwritten by AIG </u></a>, a leading global insurance organization.
            XCotton manages plan activation, claims processing, and customer support, while AIG ensures the financial
