          <ol class="nsa-accesstive" start="3">
            <li class="nsa-accesstive">
              <strong class="nsa-accesstive">3-Year Accidental Protection (provided by AIG)</strong>
            </li>
          </ol>
          <ul class="nsa-accesstive">
            <li class="nsa-accesstive">
              YarboCare™ <strong class="nsa-accesstive">5-Year Warranty</strong>also covers accidental damage not caused
