            </li>
            <li class="nsa-accesstive">Drops or collisions causing component damage</li>
            <li class="nsa-accesstive">Circuit failure due to lightning strikes or voltage surges</li>
            <li class="nsa-accesstive">Weather-related functional issues (e.g., heavy rain, hail)</li>
            <li class="nsa-accesstive">Normal wear and tear or intentional damage is excluded.</li>
          </ul>
          <ol class="nsa-accesstive" start="5">
            <li class="nsa-accesstive">
              <span class="nsa-accesstive" style="font-size: 20px;"
                ><strong class="nsa-accesstive">Door-to-Door Shipping Protection (provided by AIG)</strong></span
              >
            </li>
          </ol>
          <ul class="nsa-accesstive">
            <li class="nsa-accesstive">
              Covers loss or damage to products during transit from Yarbo's warehouse to the customer's address.
            </li>
            <li class="nsa-accesstive">Requires shipping records and damage proof for claims.</li>
            <li class="nsa-accesstive">Yarbo will repair or replace affected items at no cost.</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="nsa-accesstive">
            <strong class="nsa-accesstive">Claim Limit:</strong>The maximum total claim amount under the plan is capped
